lead_paragraph: In 2009, Lori Chalupny had a number of concussions in quick succession, causing her to take time off; now she is the second American to earn a roster spot in nonconsecutive World Cups.

headline.print_headline: Comeback For U.S. Five Years In Making
headline.main: Comeback for U.S. Women’s Soccer, Five Years in Making
